  "tips": [
    "The Espartera channel can also be a beautiful viewpoint from which we can make out the Alayos, the Trevenque or the Boca de la Pescá. All of them are peaks of medium-mountain dolomitic formations.",
    "The river of Dilar is beautiful",
    "Super nice view of the Sierra Nevada and if it gets too hot you can cool down in the Rio Dilar",
    "It is a good climb to the Collado del Fraile but it is worth it and the views are very beautiful",
    "The views will show you the highest slopes of the Sierra Nevada. They will be welcoming you to this area as you climb the first big slopes.\r\n\r\nIt depends on the time of the year, you may have snow not only on the peaks but also on the track."
